msgid "AI / Machine Learning"
msgstr "AI / Barashada Mashiinka"

msgid "Building smart systems (chatbots, automation) with tools like TensorFlow and PyTorch. Best for future tech + automation."
msgstr "In la dhiso nidaamyo caqli badan (chatbots, automation) iyadoo la isticmaalayo aaladaha sida TensorFlow iyo PyTorch. Waxay ku fiican tahay tignoolajiyada mustaqbalka iyo is-maamulidda (automation)."

msgid "Future-Ready Technology"
msgstr "Tignoolajiyada Diyaar u ah Mustaqbalka"

msgid "Next-Gen AI"
msgstr "AI-da Casriga ah (Next-Gen)"

msgid "For Smart Education"
msgstr "Ee Waxbarashada Caqliga badan"

msgid "We integrate advanced Machine Learning models to transform your institution into a data-driven powerhouse. Our systems learn, adapt, and automate so you can focus on teaching."
msgstr "Waxaan ku dhex jirnaa moodallo horumarsan oo Machine Learning ah si aan machadkaaga ugu beddelno xarun xogta ku shaqaysa. Nidaamyadayadu way bartaan, la qabsadaan, oo si toos ah u shaqeeyaan si aad diiradda u saarto waxbarashada."

msgid "Intelligent Chatbots"
msgstr "Chatbots-ka Caqliga badan"

msgid "24/7 automated support for students and parents. Handles inquiries, fee status, and schedule updates instantly."
msgstr "Taageero toos ah oo 24/7 ah oo loogu talagalay ardayda iyo waalidiinta. Waxay si degdeg ah u maamulaan weydiimaha, xaaladda ujrada, iyo cusboonaysiinta jadwalka."

msgid "Predictive Analytics"
msgstr "Falanqaynta Saadaalinta"

msgid "Identifying student performance trends and attendance risks before they become problems using TensorFlow models."
msgstr "Aqoonsiga isbeddellada waxqabadka ardayda iyo khataraha imaanshaha ka hor intaanay dhibaato noqon iyadoo la isticmaalayo moodellada TensorFlow."

msgid "Workflow Automation"
msgstr "Otomaatiga Shaqada (Workflow)"

msgid "Zero-touch processes for billing, reporting, and management. Reduce administrative overhead by up to 70%."
msgstr "Geedi-socodyo toos ah oo loogu talagalay biilasha, warbixinnada, iyo maamulka. Isku yaree culayska maamulka ilaa 70%."

msgid "AI TRAINING STATUS"
msgstr "Xaaladda Tababarka AI"

msgid "Model Accuracy"
msgstr "Saxnaanta Moodalka"

msgid "Analyzing school data patterns..."
msgstr "Falanqaynta xogta dugsiga..."

msgid "The Digital Transition"
msgstr "Kala-guurka Dijitaalka ah"

msgid "Moving from paper-based records to a cloud-native intelligence system isn’t just an upgrade—it’s a transformation. Rays Technology provides the blueprint for this evolution."
msgstr "Ka guurista diiwaannada waraaqaha ah loona guurayo nidaam caqliyeed oo daruura ah (cloud) kaliya maaha casriyeyn—waa isbeddel dhab ah. Rays Technology waxay bixisaa qorshaha isbeddelkaas."

msgid "Phase I: Digitization"
msgstr "Wajiga I: Dijitaalaynta"

msgid "Centralizing student records and financial data into a secure vault."
msgstr "Isku keenista diiwaannada ardayda iyo xogta maaliyadda meel ammaan ah oo sugan."

msgid "Phase II: Automation"
msgstr "Wajiga II: Otomaatiga"

msgid "Deploying automated billing, WhatsApp alerts, and real-time reporting."
msgstr "Hirgelinta biilasha tooska ah, ogeysiisyada WhatsApp, iyo warbixinnada wakhtiga dhabta ah."

msgid "Phase III: Intelligence"
msgstr "Wajiga III: Caqliga (Intelligence)"

msgid "Using AI to predict performance and optimize institutional resource allocation."
msgstr "Adeegsiga AI si loo saadaaliyo waxqabadka loona hagaajiyo qaybinta agabka machadka."

msgid "INSTITUTIONAL EFFICIENCY INDEX"
msgstr "TUSMAHA HUFNAANTA MACHADKA"

msgid "Trusted by Educators"
msgstr "Waxaa nagu kalsoon Macallimiinta"

msgid "Join hundreds of institutions transforming their management experience."
msgstr "Ku biir boqollaal machadood oo beddelaya habka maamulkooda."

msgid "The automated finance system changed everything for us. No more manual tracking of fees! The AI features are just a bonus."
msgstr "Nidaamka maaliyadda ee otomaatiga ah ayaa wax walba noo beddelay. Ma jiro dambe lasocodka gacanta ee ujrada! Astaamaha AI-da waa hadiyad dheeraad ah."

msgid "Registering students used to take days. Now it takes minutes. The WhatsApp integration is a lifesaver for parent updates."
msgstr "Diiwaangelinta ardaydu waxay qaadan jirtay maalmo. Hadda waxay qaadataa daqiiqado. Isku-xidhka WhatsApp-ku waa badbaado u ah cusboonaysiinta waalidiinta."

msgid "As a developer, I appreciate the clean architecture. The AI/ML capabilities are truly state of the art for this region."
msgstr "Anigoo horumariye ah, waxaan u mahadcelinayaa qaab-dhismeedka nadiifka ah. Awoodaha AI/ML runtii waa kuwa ugu casrisan gobolkan."

msgid "Common Questions"
msgstr "Su'aalaha Badanaa la Isweydiiyo"

msgid "Everything you need to know about getting started with the Rays Machad OS."
msgstr "Wax kasta oo aad u baahan tahay inaad ka ogaato bilaabista Rays Machad OS."

msgid "Still have questions?"
msgstr "Wali ma qabtaa su'aalo?"

msgid "Our support team is available 24/7 via WhatsApp."
msgstr "Kooxdayada taageerada waxay diyaar yihiin 24/7 iyadoo la isticmaalayo WhatsApp."

msgid "Contact Support"
msgstr "La xiriir Taageerada"

msgid "How long does it take to set up?"
msgstr "Muddo intee le'eg ayay qaadataa dejintu?"

msgid "Your entire school portal can be active in less than 5 minutes. We handle all the cloud infrastructure and database setup automatically."
msgstr "Dhammaan portal-ka dugsigaagu wuxuu shaqayn karaa wax ka yar 5 daqiiqo. Waxaan si otomaatig ah u maareeynaa dhammaan kaabayaasha daruuraha iyo dejinta xogta."

msgid "Is my data secure?"
msgstr "Xogtaydu ma ammaan baa?"

msgid "Yes, every institution has its own isolated database vault. We use high-grade encryption and daily backups to ensure your data is always safe."
msgstr "Haa, machad kastaa wuxuu leeyahay khasnada xogta oo gooni u ah. Waxaan isticmaalnaa sir-qarxin heer sare ah iyo koobiyo maalinle ah si aan u hubinno in xogtaadu mar walba badbaado tahay."

msgid "Can I use Somali payment methods?"
msgstr "Ma isticmaali karaa hababka lacag bixinta Soomaalida?"

msgid "Absolutely! We have native support for EVC Plus, eDahab, and Waafi integrated into the billing engine."
msgstr "Xaqiiqdii! Waxaan leenahay taageero rasmi ah oo loogu talagalay EVC Plus, eDahab, iyo Waafi oo ku dhex jira nidaamka biilasha."

